headline: GTA Online
subtitle: B-11 Strikeforce
content: Anyone can drop a kiloton of heavy ordinance from the stratosphere, but flying close air support is for the connoisseurs – and this week, they’re in for a real treat. The B-11 Strikeforce is a ten ton, twinjet delicacy dripping with missiles and explosive cannons, with countermeasures and a bomb bay available on the side. Dinner is served.
